{"tid":1320372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【仆街仔陶傑】　中國已向美國交代：「點都唔會出動解放軍！」","createTime":"2019-07-15T11:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T16:49:47.000Z","uid":14328,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"52c34dc263453f87698c1213d241d247b5c5d4ef","tid":1320372,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3010178/org/e1f2c6e26315ab31238fddc3cab7ffa9.jpg/wF48EcXdENwyGfCpJ71uUOA8VrJuf3coSumYv0rpmL8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3010178%2Forg%2Fe1f2c6e26315ab31238fddc3cab7ffa9.jpg%2FwF48EcXdENwyGfCpJ71uUOA8VrJuf3coSumYv0rpmL8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=a319c08a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n司令員陳道祥：香港事務由香港政府解決<br />\n<br />\n路透社今日（9日）發表題為《China's PLA signals it will keep Hong Kong-based troops in barracks》（中國解放軍示意會維持駐港部隊在軍營內）獨家報道，引述消息指，陳道祥與David Helvey的會面中，主動表明解放軍不會改變一直以來對港政策，軍隊不會干預港事務。消息人士對陳主動提起這個議題感到詫異，「這是一個在敏感時刻出來的明確信號。」<br />\n<br />\n報道又引述解放軍高層消息指，「香港事務由香港政府解決。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n７月１號當日陶傑嚇班後生仔話會出解放軍血洗香港立法會，搞到啲人即刻走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d7241a0d998acd9575daa0d081686194b5f2ab","tid":1320372,"uid":144522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"be water la 同埋都過咗去啦 長期抗爭黎"},{"pid":"bdc357ad0f90b0dd0f36e7283161cbeda84e52ee","tid":1320372,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52c34dc263453f87698c1213d241d247b5c5d4ef","tid":1320372,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3010178/org/e1f2c6e26315ab31238fddc3cab7ffa9.jpg/wF48EcXdENwyGfCpJ71uUOA8VrJuf3coSumYv0rpmL8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3010178%2Forg%2Fe1f2c6e26315ab31238fddc3cab7ffa9.jpg%2FwF48EcXdENwyGfCpJ71uUOA8VrJuf3